@startuml
participant User as "End User"
participant UserAgent as "User's Browser"
participant ClientApp as "Client Application"
participant AuthServer as "Authorization Server"
participant ResourceServer as "Resource Server"

note across: Initial Redirect for Authorization
User->>UserAgent: Request Access
activate UserAgent
UserAgent->>ClientApp: Request Access
deactivate UserAgent
activate ClientApp
ClientApp->>UserAgent: Redirect to AuthServer (client_id, response_type=code, redirect_uri, scope)
deactivate ClientApp
activate UserAgent
UserAgent->>AuthServer: Follow Redirect
deactivate UserAgent
activate AuthServer

note across: User Grants Consent
AuthServer->>UserAgent: Display Consent Form
deactivate AuthServer
activate UserAgent
UserAgent->>User: Display Consent Form
User->>UserAgent: Grant Consent
UserAgent->>AuthServer: Grant Consent
deactivate UserAgent
activate AuthServer
AuthServer->>UserAgent: Redirect with Authorization Code
deactivate AuthServer
activate UserAgent
UserAgent->>ClientApp: Follow Redirect with Code
deactivate UserAgent
activate ClientApp

note across: Token Exchange and Resource Access
ClientApp->>AuthServer: Exchange Code for Token
deactivate ClientApp
activate AuthServer
AuthServer->>ClientApp: Respond with Access Token
deactivate AuthServer
activate ClientApp
ClientApp->>ResourceServer: Request Protected Resource (with Access Token)
deactivate ClientApp
activate ResourceServer
ResourceServer->>ClientApp: Respond with Protected Resource
deactivate ResourceServer
activate ClientApp
ClientApp ->> UserAgent: Display Resource
deactivate ClientApp
activate UserAgent
UserAgent ->> User: Display Resource
deactivate UserAgent
@enduml
